<!ELEMENT type (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT host (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT port (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT user (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT pass (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT db (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT ssl (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT persistent (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT charset (#PCDATA)>
<!ELEMENT timeout (#PCDATA)>
